Spinister kept his whisper, "what no hello, for an old friend." he
breathed in a condescending tone. "do you want in on a job?" he
whispered again, nobody else except for Needlenose would have been able
to hear it.
______________________________________________
Hook transforms, folding up into a robot mode already facing Dreadwing.
"I'm sure he does." Hook says in a very aloof tone. He turns his nose
up, continuing his gaze. "Hear that boys. Some one wants to see us." he
says, reffering to the other Constructicons.
